@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_hfdefn(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = (tmp - wp.cos((tmp + 0.81 - tmp + 0.81)))
    v1 = 0.82
    tmp = 0.81
    v0 = wp.sin(wp.exp((v2 + 0.38 * v2 + 0.68)))
    v0 = wp.exp(wp.exp(wp.sin(tmp + 0.50)))
    v2 = (wp.sin((v2 + 0.73 / v1 + 0.14)) + ((v1 + 0.04 / tmp + 0.71) * (v0 + 0.81 + v2 + 0.82)))
    v0 = ((v0 - wp.abs(v1 + 0.31)) * (0.04 - v1))
    data[tid] = v0
